    </div>
    <section>
        <div" class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <h1 class="text-center" style="font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif">About us</h1>
                <p  class="text-center" style="font-family:'Courier New', Courier, monospace">Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Explicabo distinctio, quasi ipsam, accusantium impedit dicta earum temporibus cum beatae nihil libero perferendis expedita doloribus qui dolorem nesciunt iste, consequatur soluta?</p>
            </div>
